value.name: Man squeezed woman in ‘bear hugs’ to stop her calling police
value.description: A man charged with assault after twice wrapping his then-partner in a "bear hug" to stop her calling police on him has faced court. Joshua Douglas Strachan, 23, became emotional when the woman asked him to leave her unit and he tried to stop her from calling the police by chasing her then grabbing her from behind and "squeezing" her in a bear hug.
